# AEO Agencies

Agencies offering answer engine optimization services — from specialized AEO-first shops to full-service teams with strong AEO practices.

---

## Specialized AEO-First Agencies

These agencies lead with AEO as their core offering:

**[Get Cited](https://get-cited.ai/)**
Focused exclusively on off-site citation building. Publishes articles about your brand on the high-DA domains that ChatGPT, Claude, and Copilot index most heavily (Medium, LinkedIn Articles, major publishers). No dev access needed. Citations typically within 2–4 weeks. From $99/month.

**[Discovered Labs](https://discoveredlabs.com/)**
Technical AEO for B2B SaaS with proprietary tracking infrastructure. Documented results: 550 to 3,500+ trials in 7 weeks. Month-to-month retainers from €5,495.

**[First Page Sage](https://firstpagesage.com/)**
Claims to have launched AEO services in 2023. Clients include Microsoft, Salesforce, and Logitech. Publishes quarterly AEO studies. Strong in B2B SaaS, medtech, and healthcare.

**[Metronyx / AEO God Mode](https://aeogodmode.io/)**
The agency behind the AEO God Mode WordPress plugin. Full-service AEO strategy, schema implementation, content structuring, and monthly citation reporting.

**[Vume](https://vume.ai/aeo-agency/)**
Paris & Lisbon-based. Platform-specific optimization for OpenAI, Claude, and Perplexity alongside AI chatbots and automation. One of the few agencies that handles both AEO visibility and the conversion layer.

